graph TD
    S([Start]) --> P1[Set subtotal = 0]
    P1 --> D1{Cart Empty?}
    D1 -- Yes --> O1[/Display 'Empty'/]
    O1 --> E([Return])
    D1 -- No --> O2[/Display Header/]
    O2 --> P2[Set i = 0]
    P2 --> D2{i < cartItemCount?}
    D2 -- False --> O3[/Display Subtotal/]
    O3 --> E
    D2 -- True --> C1[[Call findProductIndexById]]
    C1 --> P3[Calculate Item Total]
    P3 --> P4[Add to Subtotal]
    P4 --> O4[/Display Item Row/]
    O4 --> P5[Increment i]
    P5 --> D2